#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:245
msgid ""
"`--max-model-len` specifies the maximum context length - that is, the sum of"
" input and output tokens for a single request. Adjust it according to your "
"actual scenario."
msgstr "`--max-model-len`指定最大上下文长度，即单个请求的输入和输出token之和。根据实际场景调整。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:246
msgid ""
"`--no-enable-prefix-caching` indicates that prefix caching is disabled. To "
"enable it, remove this option."
msgstr "`--no-enable-prefix-caching`表示禁用前缀缓存。如需启用，请移除该选项。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:247
msgid ""
"`--speculative-config` configures the MTP (Multi-Token Prediction) "
"speculative decoding to accelerate inference."
msgstr "`--speculative-config`配置MTP(多token预测)推测解码以加速推理。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:248
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables "
"full ACL graph execution in the decode phase to reduce scheduling latency."
msgstr ""
"`--compilation-config "
"'{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'`在解码阶段启用完整ACL图执行以减少调度延迟。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:249
msgid ""
"`--async-scheduling` enables asynchronous scheduling to overlap CPU "
"scheduling with NPU computation."
msgstr "`--async-scheduling`启用异步调度，使CPU调度与NPU计算重叠。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:250
msgid ""
"`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` enables the FlashComm communication "
"optimization."
msgstr "`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`启用FlashComm通信优化。"

