"本节展示DeepSeek-V4-Flash在Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)多节点环境下的部署指南，采用4\\*1P "
"1\\*4D配置以获得更优性能。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:658
msgid "Prefill node (4 P nodes share the same script)"
msgstr "Prefill节点（4个P节点共享同一脚本）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:660
msgid ""
"For each P instance, only these two configuration values need to be "
"modified: `kv_port` and `engine_id`. The `engine_id` should start from 0 and"
" increment sequentially, while the `kv_port` (e.g., `30100`) must be unique "
"for each P instance, such as 30000, 30100, etc."
msgstr ""
"对于每个P实例，只需修改两个配置值：`kv_port`和`engine_id`。`engine_id`应从0开始依次递增，而`kv_port`（例如`30100`）必须对每个P实例唯一，如30000、30100等。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:739
msgid "Decode node (4 D nodes share the same script)"
msgstr "Decode节点（4个D节点共享同一脚本）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:834
msgid ""
"For each P instance, only the `--dp-address` parameter differs and must be "
"configured as the IP address of the service within the same subnet as the "
"other instances."
msgstr "对于每个P实例，仅`--dp-address`参数不同，必须配置为与其他实例在同一子网内的服务IP地址。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:843
msgid ""
"For each D instance, only the `--dp-rank-start` parameter differs, which "
"should be configured as 0, 8, 16, and 24 respectively. Each instance's "
"`--dp-address` must be set to the IP address of the main D node, which is "
"the IP of the Decode instance with `--dp-rank-start` set to 0."
msgstr ""
"对于每个D实例，仅`--dp-rank-start`参数不同，应分别配置为0、8、16和24。每个实例的`--dp-"
"address`必须设置为主D节点的IP地址，即`--dp-rank-start`设置为0的Decode实例的IP。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:847
msgid ""
"The proxy is also implemented by referring to [Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
" (Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)."
msgstr ""
"代理也通过参考[Prefill-"
"Decode分离式部署(Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)实现。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:851
msgid ""
"`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`: enables the communication optimization "
"function on the prefill nodes."
msgstr "`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`：在prefill节点上启用通信优化功能。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:852
msgid ""
"`recompute_scheduler_enable: true`: enables the recomputation scheduler. "
"When the KV Cache of the decode node is insufficient, requests will be sent "
"to the prefill node to recompute the KV Cache. In the PD separation "
"scenario, it is recommended to enable this configuration on decode nodes."
msgstr ""
"`recompute_scheduler_enable: true`：启用重计算调度器。当decode节点的KV "
"Cache不足时，请求将被发送到prefill节点重新计算KV Cache。在PD分离场景中，建议在decode节点上启用此配置。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:853
msgid ""
"`MooncakeHybridConnector`: the KV transfer connector used for PD separation,"
" transferring KV Cache between prefill and decode nodes."
msgstr ""
"`MooncakeHybridConnector`：用于PD分离的KV传输连接器，在prefill和decode节点之间传输KV Cache。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:854
msgid ""
"`enable_shared_expert_dp: true`: enables data parallelism for shared "
"experts, applicable to MoE models."
msgstr "`enable_shared_expert_dp: true`：启用共享专家的数据并行，适用于MoE模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:856
msgid "Deployment Verification:"
msgstr "部署验证："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:858
msgid ""
"After the PD separation service is fully started, send a request through the"
" proxy port on the prefill master node to verify that Prefill and Decode "
"nodes are working correctly together. Refer to [Prefill-Decode "
"Disaggregation "
"(Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) for the "
"proxy verification method."
msgstr ""
"PD分离服务完全启动后，通过prefill主节点上的代理端口发送请求，验证Prefill和Decode节点是否协同工作正常。代理验证方法请参考[Prefill-"
"Decode分离式部署(Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:860
msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If you encounter issues with PD separation deployment, "
"please refer to the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) for "
"troubleshooting."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果遇到PD分离部署问题，请参考[公共FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html)进行故障排除。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:862
msgid "5.2.3 Ultra-Long Sequence Deployment"
msgstr "5.2.3 超长序列部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeek-V4-Flash.md:864
msgid ""
"For ultra-long sequence scenarios, support can be achieved by adjusting the "
"PD (Prefill/Decode) ratio and the model parallelism strategy. For example, "
"in a 1M sequence scenario, a 1\\*4P-1\\*4D ratio can be used, with the model"
" parallelism set to DP4TP8 mode."
msgstr ""
"对于超长序列场景，可通过调整PD(Prefill/Decode)比例和模型并行策略实现支持。例如，在1M序列场景中，可使用1\\*4P-1\\*4D比例，模型并行设置为DP4TP8模式。"

